(83425, 'sp-flock-of-familiars', '5e', 1, 'Text', 'You temporarily summon three familiars ? spirits that take animal forms of your choice. Each familiar uses the same rules and options for a familiar conjured by the Find Familiar spell. All the familiars conjured by this spell must be the same type of creature (celestials, fey, or fiends; your choice). If you already have a familiar conjured by the Find Familiar spell or similar means, then one fewer familiars are conjured by this spell.'),
(83424, 'sp-flock-of-familiars', '5e', 3, 'Text', 'When you cast a spell with a range of touch, one of the familiars conjured by this spell can deliver the spell, as normal. However, you can cast a touch spell through only one familiar per turn.'),
(83423, 'sp-flock-of-familiars', '5e', 2, 'Text', 'Familiars summoned by this spell can telepathically communicate with you and share their visual or auditory senses while they are within 1 mile of you.'),
(83422, 'sp-flock-of-familiars', '5e', 0, 'Higher Levels', 'When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you conjure an additional familiar for each slot level above 2nd.'),
