(83277, 'sp-eldritch-blast', '5e', 2, 'Higher Levels', 'The spell creates more than one beam when you reach higher levels: two beams at 5th level, three beams at 11th level, and four beams at 17th level. You can direct the beams at the same target or at different ones. Make a separate attack roll for each beam.'),
