(82973, 'sp-color-spray', '5e', 2, 'Text', 'Starting with the creature that has the lowest current hit points, each creature affected by this spell is blinded until the end of your next turn. Subtract each creatures hit points from the total before moving on to the creature with the next lowest hit points. A creatures hit points must be equal to or less than the remaining total for that creature to be affected.'),
